  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "TO : DIRECTOR, FBI DATE: July 29, 1952",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, WASHINGTON FIELD 62-0",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "SUBJECT: AERIAL OBJECTS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "\"Flying Saucers\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "INFORMATION CONCERNING",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "On July 28, 1952, at the Weekly Intelligence Conference,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Captain [REDACTED] Office of Special Investigations, 4th Air",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Force Base, Bolling Field, advised the representative of the FBI,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Washington Field Office, over the prior weekend, his office had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "received reports concerning the observation of aerial objects.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Captain [REDACTED] referred to a phone call made to his office by",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Special Agent [REDACTED] of the Washington Field Office,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "furnishing to OSI the identity of a woman who reportedly had observed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "an aerial object. [REDACTED] praised the WFO for the expeditious noti-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "fication in this instance.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Captain [REDACTED] Colonel [REDACTED] superior office,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "and Special Agent [REDACTED] in a conference on July 28,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "1952, discussed the matter of immediate notification of OSI. This",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "conference resulted in the request by Colonel [REDACTED] and Captain",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "[REDACTED] that in the event, whenever information is received by the FBI,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "in which it is alleged that someone has observed a \"Flying Saucer\",",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "this information be immediately relayed to Captain [REDACTED] office.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "It is to be noted that this office may be reached by dialing Code 1261",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "and asking for Extension 509. Captain [REDACTED] said this number should be",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "called under these circumstances at any time, day or night.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Captain [REDACTED] stated that the Air Force is greatly concerned",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "about this matter of aerial objects and said that the Air Force",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Intelligence would appreciate the execution of the requested procedure,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "mentioned above. It is suggested that the Bureau bring this matter",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "to the attention of its night supervisors, since these night supervisors",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "also receive complaints from persons outside of the Bureau and may",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "receive information concerning the observation of aerial objects.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "JMD:NPB",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
